{
  "texts": [
    "As the defualt downstream LLM, we use the Llama2-Chat-7B model finetuned for KGQA (Luo et al., 2024a).",
    "For KGQA evaluation, we adopt Hit and F1 metrics.",
    "Hit measures if any of the true answers is found in the generated response, which is typically employed when evaluating LLMs.",
    "Hit is based on exact match (Sun et al., 2024) rather than fuzzy matching as in Tan et al. (2023).",
    "F1 penalizes incorrect or missing answers."
  ]
}